Close Range				KEY:Close Range ~ Extempresario Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.ExtempresarioArcana																										DESC:You can deliver ray spells that feature a ranged touch attack as melee touch spells. You can use a ranged touch attack spell that targets more than one creature (such as Scorching Ray), but you make only one melee touch attack to deliver one of these ranged touch effects; additional ranged touch attacks from that spell are wasted and have no effect. These spells can be used with the spellstrike class feature.
Concentrate				KEY:Concentrate ~ Extempresario Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.ExtempresarioArcana																										DESC:You can reroll any concentration check you have just made with a +4 bonus. You must use this ability after the roll is made, but before the roll's outcome is determined. You must take the second roll, even if it is worse. You can use this ability once per day.
