#Extempresario ARCANA		DESC:As he gains levels, an Extempresario masters arcane secrets that supplement his magical and martial attacks. Any Extempresario who meets the prerequisites listed in a Extempresario arcana's description can select that arcana. Unless specifically noted in a Extempresario arcana's description, a Extempresario cannot select a particular Extempresario arcana more than once. Extempresario arcana that affect spells can only be used to modify spells from the Extempresario spell list unless otherwise noted in their descriptions.
